items.headline: Welcome to the Happy Harmonies Wiki
items.desc: This wiki is all about the Happy Harmonies shorts (or cartoons). It contains the episodes in the series and it also contains the characters (or creatures) in the episodes. The series was produced by Harman and Ising and the series was distributed by Metro-Goldwyn-Mayer studios. The show produced cartoons from 1934-38.
